oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Alan Boehm talks to Thomas Maupin
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Alan Boehm talks with championship buckdancer Thomas Maupin, both of Murfreesboro, TN, at the exhibit opening of Tradition: Tennessee Lives and Legacies at the Arts Center of Cannon Co. Maupin is a 2011 Tennessee Folklife Heritage Award recipient.

All photographs for the book and exhibit were taken by Nashville photographer Dean Dixon under a contract with the TAC. Editorial copy provided by Dr. Robert Cogswell, director of the TAC Folklife Program.
